snippet.textDisplay: No AI will speak to me or understand me, Siri in particular. One day I was on a tech support call trying to do an update and they wanted me to power down our office iPad. I went over to it, and since I never use it I told the tech "Ok, but I think I will need help with that.". Never even mentioned Siri, but she popped right on and said "Ok what can I help with?" and I was so irritated I just joked "Oh Siri, just go away." She said "Alright, but you could have asked nicely." and shut down. The tech support guy laughed, I laughed, and I was glad when Siri did not laugh too.
